content.text: Trial 3/5, Stage 'exit': Please describe the image and compute the stiffness matrix.

The image displays a 3D printed groove structure with the red circle marking an exit area on the lower right. We assume equal compliance to facilitate smooth egress without resistance.

**Assumptions**
1. Equal stiffness is needed along all axes.
